 off the target, to the Glasma graph\napproximation, where each quark suffers at most two gluon exchanges with the\ntarget. We find that coherent multiple scattering is essential to obtain a\npositive definite $v_2\\{4\\}$. We provide an algorithm to compute expectation\nvalues of arbitrary products of the \"dipole\" lightlike Wilson line correlators.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Jun 2017 04:06:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Jan 2018 19:23:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-31"}
