eve\n10Gbps packet I/O, and that with case studies on three stateful middleboxes, it\ncan operate at near-native speed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Jun 2017 04:07:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 4 Aug 2018 03:26:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 16 Oct 2019 02:54:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-17"}
