lar evidence estimates, but at a lower computational cost.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Jun 2017 09:52:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Oct 2017 15:38:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-16"}
